      <title>全国范围内的英国房价上涨超出了预期。</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-house-prices-rise-by-04-february-nationwide-says-2025-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据全国抵押贷款人在周五发布的数据，英国房屋价格在2月的价格上涨了比一月的0.4％，比一月的价格上涨了0.4％，这增加了买家急于下个月征收税收减免的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-house-prices-rise-by-04-february-nationwide-says-2025-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 07:08:23 GMT</pubDate>
